trans-unit.target: Replacing kegWhen replacing a keg please connect the new keg to the corresponding beer line! For example. Before cleaning you have two kegs of the same beer. Keg 1 is 50% empty. Once you have done a cleaning procedure, connect back the kegs to the corresponding beer line. Do not change the order of connection.
